《'''少男老爸'''》（{{lang-en|''Baby Daddy''}}）是[[ABC家庭|ABC家庭]]／[[Freeform|Freeform]]自製的情境喜劇影集，由[[讓-盧克·比洛多|讓-盧克·比洛多]]主演，於2012年6月20日首播(美國)。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/03/28/abc-family-has-begun-production-on-the-new-comedy-series-baby-daddy/126472/ | title = ABC Family has Begun Production on the New Comedy Series 'Baby Daddy' | first = Amanda | last = Kondolojy | date = March 28, 2012 | work = TV by the Numbers | accessdate = 2013-12-12 | archive-date = 2013-01-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130123065557/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/03/28/abc-family-has-begun-production-on-the-new-comedy-series-baby-daddy/126472/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 本劇集在2012年2月2日預訂製作。<ref name=pickup>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2012/02/02/on-the-heels-of-its-most-successful-year-on-record-abc-family-announces-the-first-portion-of-its-new-original-programming-slate-528213/20120202abcfamily01/|title=On the Heels of Its Most Successful year on Record ABC Family Announces the First Portion of Its New Original Programming Slate|date=February 2, 2012|work=The Futon Critic|accessdate=May 19, 2012|archive-date=2013-05-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gsexb8HG?url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2012/02/02/on-the-heels-of-its-most-successful-year-on-record-abc-family-announces-the-first-portion-of-its-new-original-programming-slate-528213/20120202abcfamily01/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 並於2012年3月28日開始製作。2012年8月17日，宣布本劇續訂第二季，並於2013年5月29日首播。<ref>{{cite web |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/abc-family-sets-summer-premiere-dates/ |title=ABC Family Sets Summer Premiere Dates |publisher=Deadline.com |date= |accessdate=2013-03-23 |archive-date=2013-05-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gseznkwv?url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/abc-family-sets-summer-premiere-dates/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在2013年3月22日，在第二季首播前兩個月，ABC Family電視台宣布本劇續訂第三季。<ref>{{cite web |last=Deadline |first=The |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/baby-daddy-renewed-season-3-abc-family/ |title=ABC Family Renews 'Baby Daddy' For Season 3 |publisher=Deadline.com |date= |accessdate=2013-03-23 |archive-date=2013-05-22 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Go749PIG?url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/baby-daddy-renewed-season-3-abc-family/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2014年3月17日，宣布本劇續訂第四季。<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2014/03/17/melissa-joey-baby-daddy-renewed-for-season-4-by-abc-family-network-orders-3-drama-pilots/245586/|title='Melissa & Joey' & 'Baby Daddy' Renewed for Season 4 by ABC Family & Network Orders 3 Drama Pilots|last=Bibel|first=Sara|work=TV by the Numbers|date=March 17, 2014|accessdate=March 17, 2014|archive-date=2014-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140318031227/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2014/03/17/melissa-joey-baby-daddy-renewed-for-season-4-by-abc-family-network-orders-3-drama-pilots/245586/|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 2015年2月27日宣布續訂第五季。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/02/27/baby-daddy-renewed-for-fifth-season-by-abc-family/368502/ |title='Baby Daddy' Renewed for Fifth Season by ABC Family |last=Kondolojy |first=Amanda |publisher=tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com |date=February 27, 2015 |accessdate=February 27, 2015 |archive-date=2015-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150301114344/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/02/27/baby-daddy-renewed-for-fifth-season-by-abc-family/368502/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 2016年6月27日，Freeform宣布續訂第6季。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2016/06/27/baby-daddy-renewed-season-6-danny-riley-spoilers/|title=Baby Daddy Renewed for Season 6|first1=Andy|last1=Swift|first2=Andy|last2=Swift|date=27 June 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2016-08-22|archive-date=2016-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628140006/http://tvline.com/2016/06/27/baby-daddy-renewed-season-6-d